{"tid":141244,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"歌頌盧蛇綜合區","createTime":"2017-03-02T18:14:48.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-08T08:47:10.000Z","uid":13732,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"04c8bfa7909543a4cc35b2bf2574d3c84f359649","tid":141244,"uid":13732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T18:14:48.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">盧有水出嗎? </span></span><br />\n<br />\n盧今晚有水嗎？準備出五場早水嗎？  <br />\n每晚，若不贏四場，你還算盧蛇嗎？  <br />\n<br />\n*真想跟你去買，你每天揀的波  <br />\n我每日中幾場，這算是厲害  <br />\n為何無論我，智商怎樣高  <br />\n怎樣也不可贏多你一場(怎樣也沒令自己去爭勝)  <br />\n<br />\n難道看盤看太多，看到自己confuse左  <br />\n試圖去亂鳩買，度波有咩撚用  <br />\n不懂得如何看盤口，還是我猜不透，莊家真正的心意  <br />\n<br />\n成日即場買角大，即刻停角半個鐘  <br />\n車路士正仆街，曼聯都冚家剷  <br />\n角球，成日半七全九，全班正仆街，夾埋玩鳩我*  <br />\n<br />\n盧 真係好鬼勁 日德意法西全都中  <br />\n可是沒出水比我，有甚麼撚野用？  <br />\n<br />\n難道看盤看太多，看到自己confuse左  <br />\n試圖去亂鳩買，度波有咩撚用  <br />\n不懂得如何看盤口，還是我猜不透，莊家真正的心意  <br />\n<br />\n成日即場買角大，即刻停角半個鐘  <br />\n望住佢地鳩猜，我真係把幾火  <br />\n若封盤 角大再次高水 我可能仲係 買多次角大<br />\n<a href=\"http://picosong.com/aGuN/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fpicosong.com%2FaGuN%2F&d=7QdSi1Eq0NVbLWVUesVCWJ7TfgnX9jywtYe9GXZmhCU%3D&h=7e06aa5d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://picosong.com/aGuN/</a> 巴迷子深情演繹<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">盧蛇買的波</span></span><br />\n<br />\n你要買波嗎 即出現金 <br />\n心水有曼城 這裡有共鳴 <br />\n再錯都有人聆聽 <br />\n唔撚追 任得你 更起勁 <br />\n<br />\n輸晒你想嗎 盧蛇罵你不清醒 <br />\n你仲要 更大聲 做乜勁 <br />\n<br />\nYou say 輸 撚 柒 晒 <br />\nI say 跟 實 盧 蛇 <br />\n這是盧蛇買的波 這是贏錢收的呵～ <br />\n紀錄曾經這麼收錢喔 <br />\n<br />\nYou say 輸 撚 柒 晒 <br />\nI say 跟 實 盧 蛇 <br />\n買角危險這麼多 盧蛇買咩很清楚 <br />\n慶幸曾經有人燈鳩我 至少你跟我 <br />\n<br />\n買角複雜到 不敢對賭 <br />\n開網絡地圖 不見有阿盧 <br />\n照計輸晒沒仇報 <br />\n唔撚追 沒心水 我知道 <br />\n<br />\n怕我會輸晒 便無力這麼風騷 <br />\n痛著笑 笑著哭 到蒼老 <br />\n<br />\nYou say 輸 撚 柒 晒 <br />\nI say 跟 實 盧 蛇 <br />\n這是盧蛇買的波 這是贏錢收的呵～ <br />\n紀錄曾經這麼收錢喔 <br />\n<br />\nYou say 輸 撚 柒 晒 <br />\nI say 跟 實 盧 蛇 <br />\n佢出心水這麼多 盧蛇買咩都中波 <br />\n慶幸曾經冇人燈鳩過 記得最初 <br />\n<br />\n全城鬧佢盧蛇痴線 得我貼了你勝果 <br />\n也因此我大勝 不敢唾罵 盧蛇最好<br />\n<br />\n希望繼續有人歌頌盧蛇 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"100591abf32f02477831349821725a8aa9454080","tid":141244,"uid":13732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T18:15:57.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b5b4d87e3cd0ccfa93f916e139b83cea44bc2f8","tid":141244,"uid":61463,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T18:16:18.000Z","msg":"Pish"},{"pid":"48bb297a2041a945b9dcdec17f45802d71be7b7b","tid":141244,"uid":61463,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T18:16:31.000Z","msg":"收到wind 盧好靚仔"},{"pid":"061eaf8ca463336930c01f5a498186655fe52606","tid":141244,"uid":31447,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T18:16:47.000Z","msg":"Pish"},{"pid":"f7ef19e1db1074e34e2977ccd8802a137c197649","tid":141244,"uid":4895,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T18:18:12.000Z","msg":"柒完未<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b2ef7eeb3c6ba37043daa125433d55caf19f3787","tid":141244,"uid":54482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T18:18:18.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"a6cf6b3fba4f0b3963f17f794bc6cfe802a87103","tid":141244,"uid":13732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T18:18:27.000Z","msg":"有無手吹唱第二首"},{"pid":"519d7cb177c4b859907c21ec678741f73554999c","tid":141244,"uid":31280,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T18:18:30.000Z","msg":"又黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c6bf28b4c25f21d13f3f8642d922eb002955